- [x] Explored Backup Vault settings

### 6. Security & Cost Optimization
- [x] Used **SAS tokens** to share access securely
- [x] Enabled **soft delete** for blobs and files
- [x] Used **storage tiers** (Hot, Cool, Archive) for cost control

